@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "MoreInfo";
}

<div style="text-align: center; color: #f5f5dc; padding: 40px; max-width: 1000px; margin: auto;">

    <!-- Page Heading -->
    <h2><i>More Information</i></h2>


    <!-- Integrity Section -->
    <p>
        At CMCS, integrity is the foundation of everything we do. We are committed to maintaining transparency,
        fairness, and accountability throughout the claim process. Every submission is treated with respect and
        reviewed with care to ensure that lecturers are compensated accurately and promptly.
    </p>

    <!-- Policy Section -->
    <p>
        Our policy is built around clarity and compliance. We follow institutional guidelines and ensure that
        all claims are verified through a multi-level approval process. This protects both the lecturer and the
        institution, creating a reliable and auditable workflow.
    </p>

    <!-- Trust Section -->
    <p>
        CMCS is a trustworthy platform developed with professionalism in mind. From secure document handling
        to role-based access, we ensure that every user interacts with the system confidently. Our goal is to
        make claim management seamless, secure, and stress-free.
    </p>

    <br /><br />

    <!-- What We Do Section -->
    <h3><i>What We Do</i></h3>

    <!-- Flex container for equal-sized boxes -->
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px;">

        <!-- Upload Claims Box -->
        <div style="background-color: #c2b9b0; color: black; width: 250px; height: 200px; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <h4>Upload Claims</h4>
            <p>
                Lecturers can easily upload their monthly claims along with supporting documents.
                The system ensures that all submissions are securely stored and ready for verification.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Approval Box -->
        <div style="background-color: #c2b9b0; color: black; width: 250px; height: 200px; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <h4>Approval</h4>
            <p>
                Programme Coordinators and Academic Managers review each claim for accuracy and completeness.
                Claims are approved or rejected based on institutional policy and documentation.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Status Box -->
        <div style="background-color: #c2b9b0; color: black; width: 250px; height: 200px; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <h4>Status Tracking</h4>
            <p>
                Users can track the status of their claims in real time. From submission to final approval,
                the system provides clear updates and notifications at every stage.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</div>
